15 1. I am a resident ofthe State of California. I am over the age of 18 and have personal
16 knowledge of all the facts stated herein. If called as a witness, I could and would testify
17 competently to the matters set forth below.
18 2. Since 2011, I have served as California's nonpartisan elected State
19 Superintendent of Public Instruction, and the head of the California Department of Education
20 ("CDE"). In my role, I direct all functions of CDE, act as the Secretary and Executive Officer
21 of the California State Board of Education ("SBE"), and execute the policies set by the SBE.
22 Before joining CDE I taught in Contra Costa County's Mount Diablo Unified School District
23 (where I remain a teacher-on-leave), served on the Antioch City Council, Contra Costa County
24 Board of Supervisors, and the California State Senate and State Assembly. During my tenure
25 in the California State Legislature, I acted to protect education funding, improve student
26

