18 2. I am currently employed by the California Department ofPublic Health
19 (CDPH) as the Chief of the Financial Management Branch, a position that I have held since
20 March 2, 2016.
21 3. I am familiar with the federal government's "zero-tolerance" policy and
22 Executive Order "Affording Congress an Opportunity to Address Family Separation," which I
23 understand are being challenged in this case.
24 4. The CDPH is responsible for overseeing the public health of all Californians.
25 The CDPH develops strategic policies and plans regarding issues affecting vulnerable
26

