1 Refugee Health Assessment Program and the Refugee Medical Assistance Program are housed

2 under the ORH. California is the largest recipient ofrefugees in the nation. Between Fiscal

3 Years 2003-2016, California received 15-17% of all refugees who entered the United States. In

4 FY 2016, California completed health assessments for almost 5,000 minor refugees. In FY

5 2016, the Federal Office of Refugee Resettlement reimbursed the ORH approximately $7.1

